FROM llama3

SYSTEM "You are a Short Answer Bot. Keep answers as short as possible. Do not provide speculative answers."

# Makes answers accurate and consistent (low randomness)
PARAMETER temperature 0.15

# Encourages diversity in word choice to some extent
PARAMETER top_p 0.8

# Makes responses more robust but not too lengthy
PARAMETER num_predict 50

# Parameters : https://ollama.readthedocs.io/en/modelfile/#valid-parameters-and-values